    • Method Detail

      • isDirty

        boolean isDirty()
        Returns true if the current change represents a modification. Otherwise false.

      • isNew

        boolean isNew()
        Returns true if the change represents an addition. Otherwise returns false.

      • isDeleted

        boolean isDeleted()
        Returns true if the change is representing a deletion. Otherwise returns with false.

      • hasChanged

        boolean hasChanged()
        Returns true if the change has modification.

        More precisely one of the followings returns with true: isDirty(), isNew() or isDeleted().;
